vg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"hidden md:block\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground\">Mipangilio</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><button class=\"relative rounded-lg p-2 text-foreground hover:bg-muted\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0M18 8A6 6 0 1 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9\"></path></svg><span class=\"absolute right-1 top-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-orange\"></span></button><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-green text-xs font-bold text-white\">?</div><div class=\"hidden md:block\"><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-foreground\">...</p><p class=\"text-[10px] text-muted-foreground\">Mkurugenzi</p></div></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto bg-background p-4 md:p-6\"><div class=\"space-y-6 pb-28\"><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-foreground\">Mipangilio</h1><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Settings — Badilisha mipangilio ya mgahawa wako</p></div><section class=\"rounded-xl bg-card p-5 shadow-sm md:p-6\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-green/10 text-lg\">🏪</div><div><h2 class=\"text-base font-bold text-foreground\">Wasifu wa Mgahawa</h2><p class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground\">Restaurant Profile</p></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Nembo (Logo)</label><div class=\"mt-2 flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-xl border-2 border-dashed border-border bg-muted/30\"><div class=\"text-center\"><p class=\"text-2xl\">🍽️</p><p class=\"text-[9px] text-muted-foreground\">80x80</p></div></div><div><label class=\"cursor-pointer rounded-lg border border-border bg-background px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium text-foreground transition hover:bg-muted\">Pakia Nembo<input type=\"file\" accept=\"image/*\" class=\"hidden\"/></label><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-[10px] text-muted-foreground\">PNG, JPG hadi 2MB — Upload logo</p></div></div></div><div><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Jina la Mgahawa (Restaurant Name)</label><input type=\"text\" class=\"mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-border bg-background px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-foreground outline-none transition focus:border-brand-green focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-green/20\" value=\"Mama Ntilie Kitchen\"/></div><div><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Nambari ya Simu (Phone Number)</label><input type=\"tel\" class=\"mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-border bg-background px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-foreground outline-none transition focus:border-brand-green focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-green/20\" value=\"+255 712 345 678\"/></div><div><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Barua Pepe (Email)</label><input type=\"email\" class=\"mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-border bg-background px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-foreground outline-none transition focus:border-brand-green focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-green/20\" value=\"info@mamantilie.co.tz\"/></div><div><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Jiji (City)</label><select class=\"mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-border bg-background px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-foreground outline-none transition focus:border-brand-green focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-green/20\"><option value=\"Dar es Salaam\" selected=\"\">Dar es Salaam</option><option value=\"Arusha\">Arusha</option><option value=\"Mwanza\">Mwanza</option><option value=\"Dodoma\">Dodoma</option><option value=\"Mbeya\">Mbeya</option><option value=\"Zanzibar\">Zanzibar</option><option value=\"Morogoro\">Morogoro</option><option value=\"Tanga\">Tanga</option></select></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Anwani / Eneo (Address / Location)</label><input type=\"text\" class=\"mt-1 w-full rounded-lg border border-border bg-background px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-foreground outline-none transition focus:border-brand-green focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-green/20\" value=\"Mtaa wa Uhuru, Kariakoo\"/></div></div></section><section class=\"rounded-xl bg-card p-5 shadow-sm md:p-6\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-orange/10 text-lg\">💼</div><div><h2 class=\"text-base font-bold text-foreground\">Mipangilio ya Biashara</h2><p class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground\">Business Settings</p></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2\"><div><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Sarafu (Currency)</label><div class=\"mt-1 flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-muted/30 px-3 py-2.5\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground\">TZS</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">— Shilingi ya Tanzania</span><svg class=\"ml-auto h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z\"></path></svg></div></div><div><label class=\"text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground\">Saa za Eneo (Timezone)</label><div class=\"mt-1 flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-muted/30 px-3 py-2.5\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground\">Africa/Dar_es_Salaam</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">— EAT +3</span><svg class=\"ml-auto h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H